                     <interp inst="t18430508-1405-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18430508-cd-8" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430508-1405-offence-1 t18430508-cd-8"></join>28th of April</rs>, 2 3/4 yards of fur, called squirrel flounce, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 skin, called squirrel skin, 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18430508-name-107" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-107" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
